Christian's mother, Anne, arrived a few days later, then William and Mathilde brought the newest grandchild -  Claire, nine months. We visited Mathilde and Claire one morning when all the Germains were doing family business:

<a href="http://zumsteg.us/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/DSC06035-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2366" src="http://zumsteg.us/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/DSC06035-1.jpg" alt="DSC06035-1" width="576" height="432" /></a>At the end of the week, Eric came down from his Paris digs, and we had a family dinner (family plus us, that is).

